# Owner SMS alerts, sent the moment an order is genuinely confirmed
# (COD placed, or Razorpay payment verified/captured) — via Twilio
# (https://twilio.com). Buy/verify a Twilio phone number capable of
# sending SMS to India (see https://www.twilio.com/en-us/guidelines/in/sms
# — this may need extra setup on Twilio's side), then fill these in.
# Until TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID is set, alerts are skipped (logged only) and
# checkout is unaffected.
TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=""
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=""
TWILIO_FROM_NUMBER=""
# Comma-separated, E.164 format (+<country code><number>, no spaces/dashes).
